                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9974" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2514</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2629 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">雪王的战略密码：蜜雪冰城如何打破新式茶饮上市魔咒？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Strategic Code of Snow King: How Did Mixue Ice Cream &amp; Tea Break the IPO Curse of New-style Tea Beverages?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">汤景辉，张鑫岩，苏帅轲</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">燕山大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蜜雪冰城股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蜜雪冰城；IPO上市；战略管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Mixue Ice Cream &amp; Tea; IPO listing; Strategic management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，新式茶饮行业面临“上市即破发”的魔咒困扰，奈雪的茶、茶百道、古茗等品牌上市后均遭遇严峻挑战。然而，蜜雪冰城却凭借“高质平价”战略实现强势突围，于2025年3月成功登陆港交所，首日股价飙升43.21%，市值突破千亿港元，一举打破了困扰行业的资本魔咒。本案例聚焦于蜜雪冰城冲击资本市场的战略实践：一方面通过垂直整合供应链实现核心原料自产，并自建高效智能物流体系，构建了贯穿全链路的成本优势；另一方面，精心打造“雪王IP宇宙”，实现文化情感连接。在战略布局上，坚持“农村包围城市”与全球化双轮驱动，形成了规模效应与全球化拓展并进的发展格局。历经三次资本化冲刺的淬炼，蜜雪冰城最终赢得了资本市场的认可。本案例旨在帮助学员了解蜜雪冰城如何凭借蓝海战略在竞争激烈的新式茶饮行业中突围，引导学员理解企业在快速扩张过程中，通过供应链优化、品牌IP打造及合理战略布局实现可持续价值创造的方法，同时为学员展现中国品牌以“极致性价比”与“文化认同”为双轮驱动的破局智慧。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, the new-style tea beverage industry has been haunted by the &quot;post-IPO slump&quot; curse, with brands like Nayuki, ChaPanda, and Goodme struggling post-listing. Nonetheless, Mixue Ice Cream &amp; Tea broke through with its &quot;high quality at affordable prices&quot; strategy, listing on the HKEX in March 2025. Its debut saw a 43.21% share price surge and over HK$100 billion market value, shattering the industry&#39;s capital curse.This case focuses on Mixue&#39;s capital market strategy: vertically integrating the supply chain to produce core raw materials in-house and builting an efficient smart logistics system to create full-link cost advantages. Meanwhile, it developed the &quot;Snow King IP universe&quot; to foster cultural and emotional bonds with consumers. Strategically, it adopted a dual-driven approach of &quot;encircling cities from rural areas&quot; and globalization, forming a development pattern where scale effects and global expansion advance in tandem.After three attempts at capitalization, Mixue finally gained recognition from the capital market. This case helps readers understand how Mixue achieved a breakthrough through a blue ocean strategy, offering insights into sustainable value creation via supply chain optimization, brand IP building, and rational strategic layout, showcasing Chinese brands&#39; breakthrough wisdom driven by &quot;extreme cost performance&quot; and &quot;cultural identity&quot;.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《公司战略与风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业战略的规划与执行；供应链战略的构建与应用；品牌战略的实施</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-10</td>
                            </tr>
